data.details: It is a digital platform that uses information and communication technologies in favor of promoting Cuban culture.

The National Drug Formulary registers the medicines available in Cuba, created by a group of professionals from the Ministry of Public Health with the objective of satisfying the needs of doctors, pharmacists, nurses and all professionals related to the information on medicines and their use.
The official version is the version for Android, this version for iOS was developed independently for personal use and other people who had the need to use the app but had iOS devices

The app allows you to certify that certain information existed at a particular time, it is what is called sealing time or timestamping. Take a picture or video of the car that hit you, and sign it! Are you a poet, photographer, journalist ...? You want to protect your intellectual property without spending hundreds of euros to register your work in the Intellectual Property Registry? Use this app to prove that you are the author!

Speak Slow is an online marketplace for language services where either consumer or business can get or provide language services as interpretation, translations or tutoring over the phone throughout a mobile app
This app allows manage, pair, monitor and get remote notifications from Night Owl safes

Viera Academy is a free college prep platform in a mission to democratize the path to and through college. Viera Academy Certified Tutors are endorsed by Guinness Record Holders and mental world champions.
This app allows manage, get live stream and remote notifications from DVRs devices and IP cameras

Cuba Educational Travel is a team of young Cubans and Americans working together to help the relationship between Cuba and USA through legal travel.
This application is not developed for Cuba Educational Travel and has no relationship with Cuba Educational Travel, this is just a proof of concept
The app is focused on connecting national and foreign clients with the self-employed and cooperative of Cuba
